00:47:34,280 --> 00:47:39,840
to get as many people in the door as possible. 
When you're talking to your recruiting partner,  

577
00:47:39,840 --> 00:47:44,760
they're incentivized to increase pass through 
rates, offer to close rates, all these other  

578
00:47:44,760 --> 00:47:48,240
things, and so they're like, "Yeah, this 
person's really good." And you listen. "Yeah,  

579
00:47:48,240 --> 00:47:51,800
they are pretty good, aren't they?" Even though 
there's a sneaking suspicion that maybe they're  

580
00:47:51,800 --> 00:47:56,840
not the right fit, but you move forward anyways.
So fast-forward, there's a few folks I bring on,  

581
