00:48:08,840 --> 00:48:14,560
this, that and the other. I feel terrible. How do 
I prevent this?" And the reason it's bad is not  

584
00:48:14,560 --> 00:48:20,120
just because they feel surprised, but because 
then, either one, they decide to leave, two,  

585
00:48:20,120 --> 00:48:25,240
they're not performing because it's not the 
right role or environment for them, or three,  

586
00:48:25,240 --> 00:48:29,640
maybe the company is still good, but that 
role isn't. And so they immediately try to  

587
00:48:29,640 --> 00:48:33,160
do internal mobility or something to another 
