to offer stage, I send an email with no more than  

594
00:49:08,000 --> 00:49:13,800
eight bullet points and I say all the terrible 
things that are probably going to reinforce their  

595
00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:19,440
fears. I'm pretty candid about, "This is what 
it's like here." Maybe one example would be,  

596
00:49:19,440 --> 00:49:26,080
"Hey, I'm a parent and I'm worried about 
work-life balance." Maybe they don't say that  

597
00:49:26,080 --> 00:49:30,880
explicitly in the interview process, but you get 
a feeling for it. And I get that as a parent too. 

598
00:49:31,600 --> 00:49:36,440
So if I'm at a startup, I'll be really clear 
and I'll say, "You know what? We are a series  

599
00:49:36,440 --> 00:49:42,000
A startup. We are pushing really hard at 
